市面上几百的基本都是喷雾，卖得好的是 1000+的无雾加湿器。</p>\n<p>看了下原理。这不就是十几年前那种外面一个吸水滤网中间一个风扇吗？空气净化器同问...为什么一个风扇加个滤芯这么贵</p>\n<p>因为最后肯定要买，单纯来请用过的人锤一锤，钱花的没这么痛...</p>\n<p>有推荐也可以来聊聊,目前准备买 352x50s 于是顺便锁定他家的加湿器。</p>\n","last_modified":1623894146,"replies":15,"id":783880},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1615111825","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1615111825","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":15153,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825","stars":1846,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"username":"FanChen","website":"https://ultrafine.fun","github":"AtmanChen","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53cf/02a8/211743_mini.png?m=1590733922","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/FanChen","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1485005677,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53cf/02a8/211743_mini.png?m=1590733922","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53cf/02a8/211743_mini.png?m=1590733922","location":"成都","btc":"","id":211743},"last_reply_by":"FanChen","last_touched":1623899180,"title":"使用礼品卡充值就能激活 AppleTV+ 吗？有没有老哥试过的？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/783873","created":1623893484,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1623893484,"replies":14,"id":783873},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1615111905","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1615111905","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":8578,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avata